title: Levi's Men's 505 Regular Fit Jeans (Also Available in Big & Tall)
description: LEVI'S 505: These jeans feature a classic straight leg styling created in 1967 with the original zip fly and 5 Pocket Styling.
SIZE & FIT: These 505 Regular jeans sits at the waist with a straight leg opening and designed with room in the thigh for a comfortable fit.
MATERIAL & FABRIC: Levi's 505 jeans are made from a cotton blend.
CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Machine wash cold inside out with like colors, Do not bleach, Tumble dry medium, Hot iron if needed, Dry cleaning possible.
